@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 14

title Nivelul retea: IP + protocoale de suport (overview)

rectangle "IP\n(IPv4 / IPv6)\ntransport pachete" as IP

rectangle "ARP\n(IPv4)\nIP -> MAC" as ARP
rectangle "NDP\n(IPv6)\nNS/NA, RS/RA" as NDP
rectangle "ICMP\n(IPv4)\nerori + diagnostic" as ICMP
rectangle "ICMPv6\n(erori + NDP)" as ICMP6
rectangle "DHCP\n(IPv4)\nalocare configurare" as DHCP
rectangle "DHCPv6\n(IPv6)\nconfig suplimentar" as DHCP6
rectangle "NAT / PAT\n(tranzitie IPv4)" as NAT

ARP --> IP
NDP --> IP
ICMP --> IP
ICMP6 --> IP
DHCP --> IP
DHCP6 --> IP
NAT --> IP

note bottom of IP
  IP livreaza pachete intre retele.
  Restul sunt protocoale de suport: configurare, rezolutii, erori.
end note
@enduml
